# CHANGELOG

LEGEND:
Development version <VERSION x.x.x> - <DATE> yyyy-mm-dd - Specifies latest version, not current changes in this codebase. use UNRELEASED for the date if that is the case

Development version Alpha 0.0.1 - 2026-04-13
-----------------------------------------------
- Distant Realms Game first deployment 
- Added procedurally generated world
- All game info that's needed elsewhere in the program (debug overlay usually) is located in system.game_debug and passed by the game object on initialization
- Player can move freely in an infinite world with many tile types now.
- Camera zoom can be adjusted by camera.zoom_size (this is just the tile render size)
- Second splash screen has a sick world loaded in the background with its own camera, hail modular systems

